value: Coasts of s Chile and s Argentina; ranges north to tropics
Breeds at Arauco Bay, Chile, Straits of Magellan and Tierra del Fuego. Ranges north on the western coasts of America to British Columbia and on the eastern coast of South America to Rio de Janeiro.
